description: Binghi Man Jerk Chicken specializes in authentic Caribbean Cuisine.Their signature dish is their famous hot & spicy Jamaican Jerk Chicken. They are also serving up tender mouthwatering Jamaican OxTails and Curry Goat served with fresh Steam Cabbage, Rice & Peas & Plantains. Binghi Man Jerk Chicken also has great vegetarian options as well. "Bringing a little Jamaica to You" Yeah Mon!
name: Binghiman Jerk Chicken
